'''''Applied Geochemistry''''' is an international [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by the [[International Association of GeoChemistry]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iagc-society.org/applied_geochemistry.html|title=Applied Geochemistry|author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2010 |website=www.iagc-society.org|publisher=International Association of GeoChemistry |access-date=18 October 2018 |quote=}}</ref> covering research on [[geochemistry]] and [[urban geochemistry]] that was established in 1986. It is published by [[Elsevier]] and the [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Michael Kersten]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.journals.elsevier.com/applied-geochemistry|title=Applied Geochemistry|author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2018 |website=www.journals.elsevier.com |publisher=Elsevier |access-date=18 October 2018 |quote=}}</ref>
