{{Infobox oil field | name = Tokarevskoye | country = [[Kazakhstan]] | region = [[West Kazakhstan Province]] | location = | block = | offonshore = onshore | location_map = Kazakhstan | location_map_width = | location_map_text = | coordinates = {{coord|51|07|N|50|12|E|region:KZ_type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | coordinates_ref = | operator = Joint Venture Stepnoy Leopard, Ltd | operators = | partners = | contractors = | image = | caption = | discovery = 1969 | start_development = | start_production = | abandonment = | peak_year = | peak_of_production_oil_bbl/d = | peak_of_production_oil_tpy = | peak_of_production_gas_mmcuft/d = | peak_of_production_gas_mmscm/d = | peak_of_production_gas_bcm/y = | oil_production_bbl/d = | oil_production_tpy = | production_year_oil = | production_gas_mmcuft/d = | production_gas_mmscm/d = | production_gas_bcm/y = | production_year_gas = | est_oil_bbl = | est_oil_t = | recover_oil_bbl = | recover_oil_t = | est_gas_bft = | est_gas_bcm = | recover_gas_bft = | recover_gas_bcm = | formations = }}
The '''Tokarevskoye gas condensate field''', 80&nbsp;km west of [[Uralsk]], consists of four individual accumulations whose productivity is proved by several wells. Gas water surface of some deposits range between 2776–2082 m.<ref>[http://geology.gov.kz/ru/pomosh-biznesu/reference-fields-in-kazakhstan/menu-oil-gas-deposit/item/%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B2%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B5?category_id=15 Tokarevskoye gas condensate field<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060631/http://geology.gov.kz/ru/pomosh-biznesu/reference-fields-in-kazakhstan/menu-oil-gas-deposit/item/%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B2%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B5?category_id=15 |date=2013-09-21 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.condensat.kz/64.html?&L=%272 History of geological association "Uralskneftegazgeologiya" <!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.leo.isd.kz/page.php?page_id=49&lang=2 About company "Joint Venture "Stepnoy Leopard, LTD"<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref>
